titles.title: To extend the temporary suspension of duty on 1/ 3-Phenyl-7-(4-propoxyphenyl)benzoY1,2-b:4,5-b?difuran- 2,6-dione.

bill.summary:
2/7/2008--Introduced.
Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend the temporary suspension of duty on 1/ 3-Phenyl-7-(4-propoxyphenyl)benzoY1,2-b:4,5-b?difuran- 2,6-dione.
